=head2 Strftime Patterns

=head3 %c (%A፣ %B %e መዓልቲ %Y %r %Z) - date time format

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ሰሉስ፣ ለካቲት  5 መዓልቲ 2008 06:30:30 ድ.ቀ. UTC
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = ዓርቢ፣ ታሕሳስ 22 መዓልቲ 1995 09:05:02 ቅ.ቀ. UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = ቀዳም፣ መስከረም 15 መዓልቲ -10 04:44:23 ቅ.ቀ. UTC

=head3 %x (%d/%m/%Y) - date format

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05/02/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/09/-10

=head3 %X (%l:%M:%S %p) - time format

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 =  6:30:30 ድ.ቀ.
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 =  9:05:02 ቅ.ቀ.
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 =  4:44:23 ቅ.ቀ.

=head1 SUPPORT

See L<DateTime::Locale>.

=cut
